The initial structure of `skills/article-reader/` — including SKILL.md,
references/methodology.md, references/template.org — and the `.claude-plugin/`
metadata were imported verbatim from the upstream project.

Subsequent commits adapt this code to a different design goal: transforming
the original batch analysis workflow into an interactive forcing-question
reading companion anchored to an Obsidian vault. See DESIGN.md for the full
rationale.
